   "source": [
    "# Learning Rate Experiments for Vanilla DQN\n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook runs a learning-rate ablation study for the vanilla DQN LunarLander baseline. All baseline parameters are kept fixed except `learning_rate`.\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. Setup and Imports\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
   "metadata": {
    "ExecuteTime": {
     "end_time": "2026-05-23T06:46:08.902175500Z",
     "start_time": "2026-05-23T06:46:08.877840900Z"
    }
   },
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "Using device: cpu\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "import sys\n",
    "import os\n",
    "import pickle\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "\n",
    "sys.path.insert(0, os.path.abspath('..'))\n",
    "\n",
    "from core.vanilla_dqn_lunar_lander import (\n",
    "    train_dqn,\n",
    "    evaluate_dqn,\n",
    "    save_plot,\n",
    "    save_results,\n",
    "    save_model,\n",
    ")\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 2. Experiment Settings\n",
    "\n",
    "Keep the vanilla baseline settings unchanged and vary only the learning rate.\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "metadata": {
    "ExecuteTime": {
     "end_time": "2026-05-23T06:46:09.176496100Z",
     "start_time": "2026-05-23T06:46:08.905345900Z"
    }
   },
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "learning_rates = [3e-3, 2e-3, 1e-3, 8e-4, 7e-4, 5e-4, 3e-4, 1e-4, 5e-5]\n",
    "num_episodes = 500\n",
    "num_eval_episodes = 10\n",
    "\n",
    "# ======== Multi-seed experiment setup ========\n",
    "# Use the same five seeds for every learning rate so the comparison is fairer.\n",
    "seeds = [0, 1, 2, 3, 4]\n",
    "# ======== End multi-seed experiment setup ========\n",
    "\n",
    "base_hyperparameters = {\n",
    "    'batch_size': 32,\n",
    "    'update_frequency': 4,\n",
    "    'target_update_frequency': 100,\n",
    "    'num_layers': 2,\n",
    "    'hidden_dim': 128,\n",
    "    'epsilon_decay': 0.995,\n",
    "    'gamma': 0.99,\n",
    "    'num_episodes': num_episodes,\n",
    "    'num_eval_episodes': num_eval_episodes,\n",
    "    'seeds': seeds,\n",
    "}\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 3. Run Learning Rate Ablation\n",
